C:\Program Files (x86)\Windows Kits\10\include\10.0.18362.0\um\commctrl.h(1215,17): error: expected ';' after top level declarator
} TBBUTTON, NEAR* PTBBUTTON, *LPTBBUTTON;
                ^
C:\Program Files (x86)\Windows Kits\10\include\10.0.18362.0\um\commctrl.h(2254,16): error: typedef redefinition with different types ('struct tagTOOLINFOA' vs 'struct _TBBUTTON')
} TTTOOLINFOA, NEAR *PTOOLINFOA, *LPTTTOOLINFOA;
               ^
C:\Program Files (x86)\Windows Kits\10\include\10.0.18362.0\um\commctrl.h(1215,13): note: previous definition is here
} TBBUTTON, NEAR* PTBBUTTON, *LPTBBUTTON;
            ^
